{"tid":1405462,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"得閒就要關心下身邊嘅人啦","createTime":"2019-08-04T09:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:58:19.000Z","uid":298071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6e1d7eb2cabc93a4b988ca65f317938d7cfb9966","tid":1405462,"uid":298071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:48:52.000Z","msg":"P牌出post 多多包涵<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">上天有好生之德 今見港豬橫行 唯望普渡眾生 淨化世人</div></span></strong></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fe9TUdM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffe9TUdM.png&h=e22df9bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作為一個心理學嘅學生我可以話比大家聽朋輩嘅支持同鼓勵真係有好大嘅作用架<br />\n由其系 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">University of Bristol</span></span></strong> 嘅同學仔要更加關心你嘅同學啊<br />\n<br />\n以下亦開放各位同路人互相打氣及本人比大家做樹窿(唔好搞我後面 <br />\n我地要一齊until dawn啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<del><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">慈愛的聖光 照耀一切</span></span></div></del><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"b4e9afc067381363f1d77d453500f2cfca25d0f5","tid":1405462,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:58:19.000Z","msg":"8月5日 全港罷工罷市罷買"}]}